channel.title: Compiling errors
channel.description:
Hey. I'm using Testscape and whenever I compile I get this error:
[code]Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: server Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Could anybody help? If so, thanks.
